---
/**
 * Featured Insight banner for the homepage.
 * Links to the latest data-driven article.
 */
---

<section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-surface-dark via-[#1a1510] to-surface-dark border-y border-owr-gold-dark/20 dark:border-owr-gold-dark/20">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8 md:py-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-6 md:gap-10">
      <!-- Icon/Badge -->
      <div class="flex-shrink-0">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-owr-gold/20 to-owr-gold/5 border border-owr-gold-dark/30 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-owr-gold" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 3v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 6 16.5h2.25M3.75 3h-1.5m1.5 0h16.5m0 0h1.5m-1.5 0v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 18 16.5h-2.25m-7.5 0h7.5m-7.5 0-1 3m8.5-3 1 3m0 0 .5 1.5m-.5-1.5h-9.5m0 0-.5 1.5m.75-9 3-3 2.148 2.148A12.061 12.061 0 0 1 16.5 7.605" />
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-left">
        <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-owr-gold-dark mb-1">Featured Insight</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">The Renegade Effect</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 max-w-2xl">
          With Renegades v2.0 on the horizon, we dug into 13 months of global tournament data to answer the question:
          did v1.0 actually make a difference? 1,097 tournaments. 15,697 player results. Here&apos;s our take.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <a
        href="/insights/renegade-effect"
        class="flex-shrink-0 inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-owr-gold hover:bg-owr-gold-dark text-gray-900 font-semibold text-sm rounded-lg transition-colors cursor-pointer"
      >
        Read the Analysis
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
